body: It is because your path for the study folder doesnt need to include the annual simulation. You just need the path up the east shade and you specify the study type (for annual simulation, it should be 5 ). Then you just have to refresh it and everything should look great. [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/cYJbDW7C4z4-M1wJ9QA4dBjV9YXJ7n9sN8AvmW2MRusqC0YZTwHUlfrqQrQSqmBQmj35NdYi5jRiPsWm6wpdGSSvO9AC-83-/Capture.PNG)
